Debian

Required Packages

Needs the following packages installed:

build-essential
cmake
g++ (not used by project but cmake complains otherwise)
pkg-config

libdb-dev
libxml2-dev

Optional Packages

librpm-dev

Building
==========

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
sudo make install

Debug
======

Can enable debugging by passing the -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug option on
the cmake command line.
